<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>ZeroBench Time - Welcome</title>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #fbfbfb; font-family: arial, sans-serif;">
  <div style="width: 620px; margin: auto; padding: 10px 0">
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 12px; width: 100%; table-layout: fixed;">
      <tr>
        <td style="text-align: center;">
          <img src="https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1glJskRh377ns11muSy-sdPBOii9i6l7o" width="160" alt="ZeroBenchTime" title="ZeroBenchTime">
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"
      style="border-radius: 6px; background-color: white; text-align: center;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 30px;">
          <h1 style="font-family: arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-stretch: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            line-height: 1.15;
            letter-spacing: normal;
            margin: 10px 0 20px;
            text-align: center;">Welcome!</h1>
          <p style="
            font-family: arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-stretch: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            line-height: 1.38;
            letter-spacing: normal;
            color: #bababa;
            margin: 0 0 30px;
            text-align: center;">
            Hi! Thanks for signing up with us. From now on, you’ll get regular updates on new listings and
            consultants
            and since you’ll be the first to know, you can always take a first move to optimise or hire someone for your
            work.</p>
          <a href="{{{link}}}" style="padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: white;
            background-color: #2b97f7;
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: arial, sans-serif;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            width: 140px;">Verify</a>
          <br/>
          <p style="
            font-family: arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-stretch: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            line-height: 1.38;
            letter-spacing: normal;
            color: #bababa;
            margin: 0 0 30px;
            text-align: center;">
            Thanks, <br />
            The ZeroBenchTime Team
